  "intent": "Execute slide array spotting protocol using multichannel P300 pipette to transfer samples from up to 4 x 96-well plates onto microscope slides. Perform initial wash and blot sequence using 4-reservoir wash system and blot paper. For each sample column, dip pipette tips 3 times into source wells at specified height, then contact slide surface for defined dwell time. Between each sample transfer, execute wash cycle with vertical agitation or static wash, followed by blotting on absorbent paper with controlled Z-axis and aspiration speeds.",
